nodes.text: The Dorande system was a star system located in the Quiberon sector of the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories that contained the planet Dorande, the homeworld of the sentient species of the same name.
The Dorande system was established in The Essential Atlas, a reference book written by Jason Fry and Daniel Wallace and released on August 18, 2009, which placed the system in grid square T-15.
